# Regex allowlist for .github/scripts/check-design-token-css.sh
#
# Rules are matched against full rg output lines in this format:
# path/to/file.css:line-number:line-content
#
# Keep rules narrow and file-scoped to avoid masking real violations.
# Example:
# ^libs/shared/ui-legacy/src/legacy/legacy\.css:[0-9]+:.*#[0-9A-Fa-f]{6}\b
